        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Mumbai/scene_mongoose.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 80051c02-e026-40fe-970a-7b7aaa62302c).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning, 47. Our ally Dawood Rangan has been told that the local hitman and operative for the very large Silence Mafia, &quot;The Kashmirian&quot; has been told to carry out a hit on him. He is convinced it all points to the mafia. While you are there, he would like you to kill &quot;Satish Jagannath&quot;, another member of the mafia who has collected evidence that would hurt Rangan&apos;s reputation. Finally, take out &quot;Rajesh Varma&quot;, a high ranking mafia member who has a document on why Rangan is a target.",
